{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_03_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚 2話 私にしか出来ないこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "渚、調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are things going‚ Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～、なんだか\nどんどん深みにハマってる気がします……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…\nIt’s like I’ve backed myself into a corner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "大食いキャラはどうかなって琴乃ちゃんに聞いたら\n「やめておいた方がいいと思う」って苦笑いされて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked Kotono-chan about me establishing a big eater personality.\nShe gave me a wry smile and said‚ “I don’t think that’s a great idea.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.56495079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まだ目指してたのか……\n本当に、無理はしないでくれよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re still on that plan?\nYou really shouldn’t force yourself‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "その次は、アイドルっぽい個性的な趣味を\n見つけようと思いまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Other than that‚ I was thinking about discovering\nsome kind of unique hobby that’s idol-like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんに相談したら\nそれなら一緒に趣味を探そうって話になったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I discussed this with Haruko-san\nand we talked about discovering a hobby together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いいことじゃないか\nそれで、どうなったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like a good start.\nHow did it go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……気付いたら、二人で盆栽の記事を眺めた後\nメイク動画のバズらせ方について議論してました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we started the day reading up articles on miniature bonsai\nand ended the day with a heated discussion on how to get views for make-up videos.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "振り幅が大き過ぎるな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a really wide range of topics…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ひ～……{user}さぁ～ん……\n私やっぱりダメかもしれませ～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*… {user}-saaaan…\nI don’t think I can do this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7819033073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと私はこれから一生無個性アイドルとして\n生きていくんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be stuck as an idol without a personality\nfor the rest of my life…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　それはそれで親近感があっていいのかも？\nいやでも、そもそも見つけてもらえないことには……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Maybe that will give people a sense of kinship!\nWait‚ no‚ first you have to get noticed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ迷走してるな……ちょっと待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sound like you’re pretty lost… Wait here a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ\nまぁ、これを食べて元気を出してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here you go.\nEat up. You’ll feel better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "わわ、桃が丸ごとお皿に！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ is that a whole peach on the plate?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "期間限定で販売されてるスイーツなんだ\n食べてみてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a special dessert they were selling for a limited time only.\nTry it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "凄い……中にカスタードクリームと、いちごまで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! It’s filled with custard and strawberries!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "いただきま～す……あむ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! Mmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "んふ～……！　おいひぃれす……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… it’s so good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "今度琴乃ちゃんと一緒に食べたいです\n素敵なお菓子を教えてくれてありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanna eat it together with Kotono-chan next time.\nThank you for letting me know about this sweet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はは、渚は本当に琴乃が好きだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha! You really are fond of Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！\n私はずっと琴乃ちゃんを見てきたんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nWe’ve been friends for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんとの思い出もばっちり記録してますし……あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I keep a record of all my memories with her… Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、あれを見返せば……何か分かるかも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe I can get some ideas by reading them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "渚、何か掴めたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a plan‚ Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "まだどうなるか分からないですけど……\n前に進める、かもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m not entirely sure where this will lead to…\nBut this could be a way forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、それならよかった\nさぁ、沢山食べてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Glad to hear that.\nGo on‚ tuck in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　……んふ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! Mmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.666666699995,
          "startTime": 149.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_night",
      "startTime": 149.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "わー、こんなことあったっけなー\nふふ、懐かしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yeah‚ this happened…\nHehe. This brings back memories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
